snippet.title: Koi Unleashed gameplay teaser
snippet.description:
Gameplay teaser trailer for PC game Koi Unleashed.

Koi Unleashed is an action RPG, with party-based combat and inspired by Japanese folklore.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1128310/Koi_Unleashed/
Itch.io: https://wildgrip.itch.io/koi-unleashed
Website: https://wild-grip.com/koi-unleashed
